text: Oops!... I Did It Again is the second album released by American pop music singer Britney Spears on Jive Records. Four singles were released from the album, the title track, "Lucky", "Stronger", and "Don't Let Me Be The Last To Know". It also features the first song Britney had a hand in writing, titled "Dear Diary". Category:2000 albums Category:Britney Spears albums
title: Oops!... I Did It Again
